<headline>Heat Advisory issued May 28 at 9:47AM MDT until May 28 at 8:00PM MDT by NWS Albuquerque</headline>
<description>...HEAT ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT FROM 1 PM THIS AFTERNOON TO 8 PM
MDT THIS EVENING...
* WHAT...Temperatures up to 103 to 105 expected.
* WHERE...Chaves County Plains.
* WHEN...From 1 PM this afternoon to 8 PM MDT this evening.
* IMPACTS...Hot temperatures may cause heat illnesses.</description>
<instruction>Drink plenty of fluids, stay in an air-conditioned room, stay out of
the sun, and check up on relatives and neighbors.</instruction>
